{"tid":544660,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"[I/A] King's Raid #71 連登五星專第一人-刷手刷首抽巴打","createTime":"2018-01-29T17:36:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-30T01:31:33.000Z","uid":49449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"066bbf7d13d3cf52927f8cc313c6859f904f247a","tid":544660,"uid":49449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T17:36:43.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">Server【Asia】</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/15/141711_dedcc7b9deea6af5d8691a925b55be6f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F15%2F141711_dedcc7b9deea6af5d8691a925b55be6f.png&h=72e0e3c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\"><strong>新手巴絲<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好</span></span>亂入公會，要入就入Lihkg公會<br />\n因為你一入錯，要退會入Lihkg公會，就要等足七日先會有奬勵你拎<br />\n唔使問有無位，搵到即係有，搵唔到即係無<br />\n申請咗邊個公會+ID麻煩填表，優先處理填表巴絲<br />\n填完麻煩再係Post度留名話自己填咗表，即有專人為你服務</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong>【公會】申請表/請假表</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">麻煩新手巴絲睇咗全攻略先，睇完有咩唔明再問，所有攻略僅供參考</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>【LIHKG】King's Raid 全攻略<br />\n【集各巴之大成】</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">【LIHKG】King&rsquo;s Raid 裝備系統簡介</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>【LIHKG】King Raid's 歐洲人逐個捉</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\"><strong>【LIHKG】King's Raid Friend List</strong></span></span><br />\n歡迎各巴絲留低ID 加好友啦喂<br />\n(記得每日送心先有本錢溝囡)<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">ANDROID</span></strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://apps.qoo-app.com/app/4943\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapps.qoo-app.com%2Fapp%2F4943&d=btCVXQQjrXwPBq5llfxgH7%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=3387c788\" target=\"_blank\">https://apps.qoo-app.com/app/4943</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">IOS</span></strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/kings-raid/id1097735195\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fitunes.apple.com%2Fus%2Fapp%2Fkings-raid%2Fid1097735195&d=btCVXQQjrXwPBq5llfxgH7%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=5ab58154\" target=\"_blank\">https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/kings-raid/id1097735195</a><br />\n<br />\nQ：英雄自選劵揀咩英好?<br />\nA：有愛&gt;一切<br />\n依隻驚無勁唔勁，只有夾唔夾<br />\n同埋官方會因應英雄強弱而作出Buff同Nerf嘅調整<br />\n今個版本可能弱勢啲，但下個版本可能變神角都未定<br />\n所以不如揀咗有邊隻英係你真係鍾意嘅，想用嘅<br />\n再係Post度問下有咩組合可以夾佢，咁會比較好<br />\n相信各巴絲都好樂意為新手巴絲們解答的<br />\n<br />\nQ：我抽到依樣嘢又唔係專武，咁係咩嚟?<br />\nA：Artifact<br />\n英文版：<a href=\"https://maskofgoblin.netlify.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmaskofgoblin.netlify.com&d=btCVXQQjrXwPBq5llfxgH7%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=294312ef\" target=\"_blank\">https://maskofgoblin.netlify.com</a><br />\n殘中版：<a href=\"http://bbs.ngacn.cc/read.php?tid=12943067\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbbs.ngacn.cc%2Fread.php%3Ftid%3D12943067&d=btCVXQQjrXwPBq5llfxgH7%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=c6d28677\" target=\"_blank\">http://bbs.ngacn.cc/read.php?tid=12943067</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/27/225213_b0ebf846580f6d4fd30174af7c4c201d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F27%2F225213_b0ebf846580f6d4fd30174af7c4c201d.jpg&h=70b636b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nQ：需唔需要刷首抽架？<br />\nA：無首抽依回事，因為唔係抽返嚟，係可以直接用英雄自選卷換返嚟(新英除外)<br />\n【新手一定會有一張二星同三星英雄自選劵】<br />\n<br />\nQ：幾LV封頂？<br />\nＡ：80，英雄1至80級所需經驗<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/veW4Zw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FveW4Zw&d=btCVXQQjrXwPBq5llfxgH7%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=ce71a13f\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/veW4Zw</a><br />\n<br />\n如有更多問題可詳見【LIHKG】King's Raid 新手入門或回覆<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div>"},{"pid":"1405a1f9f7a1d5e7b067aacaca082b7bd6882da6","tid":544660,"uid":49449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T17:37:29.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div>"},{"pid":"1b2fbf59b8e87a1ef502170001d842d247d5f26e","tid":544660,"uid":49449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T17:37:53.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/25/174136_ff7c346f99a63bccc8a62e1d2b2671bc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F25%2F174136_ff7c346f99a63bccc8a62e1d2b2671bc.png&h=f3107096&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nHello!<br />\n<br />\nThis is GM Luna!<br />\nWe have prepared an event page for Pre- Register to celebrate our 1 year anniversary!<br />\nWe have lots of rewards and events ready to be shown, please participate in our awesome Pre-Register!! ◟( ˘ &sup3;˘)◞ ♡<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nThe details are as followed.<br />\n--------------------------------------------------------<br />\nOur Event Noti