</strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">- Participation Period: &ndash; Feburary 11th 2018</span><br />\n- Reward: 7 Types of Fragments x100 / Special Summon (x10) x3 / 10 Million Gold<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">※ Pre-Register Event Reward will be sent into mailbox within 7 days &lsquo;AFTER&rsquo; the end of the event.</span> <br />\n<br />\n&ndash; You can participate this event only once per account.<br />\n&ndash; You can claim the reward from the mail until 23:59 February 28th 2018. <br />\n- You can participate in 1 Year Anniversary Pre-Register event regardless of which app market (Apple/ Google) you use.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>★Event #2!!! Share the 1 Year Anniversary Event Page in FacebooK! ★<br />\n</strong></span><br />\nThe more people participate in Pre-Register Event, the more rewards you receive~~~♪<br />\n<br />\nIf you have participated Event #1 Pre-Register Event, please <span style=\"color: red;\">share King&rsquo;s Raid 1 year anniversary celebration via FacebooK!!</span><br />\n<br />\n☆Reach <span style=\"color: red;\">50,000</span> Pre-Register: <span style=\"color: red;\">1000 Rubies!</span><br />\n☆Reach <span style=\"color: red;\">100,000</span> Pre-Register: <span style=\"color: red;\">Special Summon (x10) x1</span><br />\n☆Reach <span style=\"color: red;\">150,000</span> Pre-Register: <span style=\"color: red;\">T1 Hero Ticket x1 </span><br />\n(Only those heroes released <span style=\"color: red;\">before December 20th 2017</span>)<br />\n☆Reach <span style=\"color: red;\">200,000</span> Pre-Register: <span style=\"color: red;\">Unique Weapon Ticket x1 </span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>★Event #3!!! 1 Year Anniversary of King&rsquo;s Raid GLOBAL Release! Special Attendance Event!★</strong></span><br />\n<br />\nOur <span style=\"color: red;\">Special Attendance Event starts from 12th of February</span> to celebrate Global Release 1 Year Anniversary!<br />\n[King&rsquo;s], [Raid], [Vespa]<br />\nWe have these 3 types of gifts awaiting you. ^ㅡ^<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">You can collect 1 of the 3</span> once you login <span style=\"color: red;\">on 12th of February</span>.<br />\n※ This Special Attendance Event for 1 Year Anniversary may have some changes. <br />\n- Any<span style=\"color: red;\"> players</span>  who have their King&rsquo;s Raid <span style=\"color: red;\">first log in after February 12th</span> will see <span style=\"color: red;\">[King&rsquo;s] attendance sheet</span><br />\n- Any updates regarding this 1 Year Anniversary Special Attendance Event will be shared via notice in our official community. <br />\n<br />\nWe hope you all enjoy this Pre-Register Event with King's Raid!! <br />\n<br />\nWith Love, GM Luna.</div>"},{"pid":"0649b5aead2ebeaa7696395c5879e40482f04880","tid":544660,"uid":116537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T23:05:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/30/070523_5d441a8e34d577bcda55aab628b17e12.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F30%2F070523_5d441a8e34d577bcda55aab628b17e12.png&h=ad03ffb7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/30/070526_888ead976b216b8c115fdeb6bc842f57.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F30%2F070526_888ead976b216b8c115fdeb6bc842f57.png&h=d97c39a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n趕得切月尾魔隊過關<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7dc5f8962eef95c6f38e18ca2f58d1f02faf1294","tid":544660,"uid":169075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T23:22:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/30/071820_1d